{"tid":2212282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國跨黨派議員致函外相　促對BNO護照持有人提供領事保護","createTime":"2020-09-21T16:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T00:47:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ec6774776db479b2621b408ea09dea1433973c","tid":2212282,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200921/photo/bkn-20200921232203743-0921_00912_001_01p.jpg?20200921232406\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200921%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200921232203743-0921_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20200921232406&h=03c8acc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒周一（21日）報道，英國跨黨派議員早前去信外相藍韜文，指在港英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）持有人，在《港區國安法》下被捕後可能送往中國大陸審訊，因此要求藍韜文會面，商討對該批人提供領事保護事宜。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》報道，信件內容指由於中國政府表明有意阻止涉嫌違反《港區國安法》的人離開香港，因此英國政府早前提出擴大BNO護照持有人居權及提供申請入籍途徑，對於最可能因觸犯《港區國安法》而被捕的人幫助十分輕微。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交政策智庫執行董事門多薩（Alan Mendoza）指，英國不可以一方面聲稱要捍衞英國海外國民的權利，但在他們最需要領事援助時，拒絕提供有關協助。英國外交部指，當政府相信香港人民自由受削弱，會繼續發聲和致力維護港人權利。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200921/bkn-20200921232203743-0921_00912_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"219d6727a8e954c226ba0167d80278251fbdd7bd","tid":2212282,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b4c21498d4ff62f798e08bf6f85c1a03f7c3d3","tid":2212282,"uid":23061,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T19:41:03.000Z","msg":"即轉BC啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過又畀啲傻閪話「貼埋張大床你訓好冇」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3f05bfa3e91129dfbfda91bd631940c1922a61","tid":2212282,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":